result.name: Ma Sa Restaurant

reviews.text: Good egg and spam for a decent price (37 hkd). I went at 1 and they ran out of the BBQ pork. The owner can speak a bit of English. I don't know if they have an English menu but I just showed them pictures which is what someone else here recommended. Limited seating and you may need to wait. Good sized portions.

Very good hole in the wall. Very simple dish with 3 eggs on a nest of white rice and some slices of ham with soya sauce. But wow the taste is very good. Very homy. Seems very local. 37 hkd reasonable price for Hong Kong Island

About as local as it gets in Hong Kong. They speak limited English (or rather, I had limited Cantonese), but you can get by fine with pointing or showing them pictures of what you want. They are famous for their spam and eggs. The price is eye wateringly cheap.

So lucky man !!!!
When I take order Charsiew Egg rice , that is a last one !!! 

Sunday 1.35pm

One of my favourite chow in HK .. edited in 2019 to reflect how much I love this place. If i have 2 hours in HK ... I'll be here for a meal. It's that good for something so simple (luncheon meat, eggs and rice).. and the 干炒牛河 is not too bad too. I really love this place!

reviews.text: Good egg and spam for a decent price (37 hkd). I went at 1 and they ran out of the BBQ pork. The owner can speak a bit of English. I don't know if they have an English menu but I just showed them pictures which is what someone else here recommended. Limited seating and you may need to wait. Good sized portions.
제일 유명한 아침으로 계란과 스팸 덮밥 먹으러 갔는데 11시 이후부터 된다고 해서 그냥 햄샌드위치 세트 먹었음 ! 현지 차찬탱 문화 즐기기 좋을듯 ! 맛은 중간 !!

Três ovos fritos e uma farta porção de char siu em cima do arroz. Uma refeição farta de proteína e de muita energia. Para poucos, muitos asiáticos dão nota baixa pois em geral consomem pratos mais leves. Eu adorei!

【煎蛋午餐飯】5星
午餐肉，3顆太陽蛋，醬汁，雖然叉燒很不怎麼樣，但是整體搭配起來的平衡美味，已經烙印在我靈魂深處，5顆星，還是只能給5星，好吃，真好吃。

2019.05.18 2訪，午餐肉煎製品質不一，有時會煎得很乾，口感較差，有時濕潤，今天就不比較乾。
價錢中等，員工態度平平，味道同普通茶餐一樣，三蛋飯言過其實，其他炒類食品相對較好
